wrote:
>
>
> .doc, .rtf, even .txt would be fine - PDF is by design not editable.
>
> That's what I love about some of these pieces; the memory is not mine,
but it somehow evokes the same sensation. That's valuable, especially if it
affects others similarly.
>
> - J
>
